# Volunteering Opportunities Telegram Notifier


## Description

This is a telegram bot that scrapes health volunteering opportunities in Saudi Arabia and notifies subscribed users according to their selected cities  

## Use

Currently not hosted to be used by the public

If you are interested in developing it more, clone the project and run:

```
# Set the database credentials in .env file along with bot token
cp .env.example .env
# Install the packages
npm install
# Migrate the database
npm run migrate
```

